data.description: Here’s your chance to own this amazing 4 bedroom ranch located in a quite and peaceful neighborhood with NO HOA! This is a rare opportunity to own a little over a 1/4 of an acre so close proximity to Downtown Troutman and Troutman Elementary and Middle Schools. Discover the spacious open floor plan with high ceilings creating a warm and inviting atmosphere thru thoughtfully designed interior that maximizes space and natural light, beautiful hardwoods adds a touch of elegance, dining adorned with wainscoting provides a sophisticated backdrop for your meals, Breakfast, primary with garden tub and separate shower plus Kitchen equipped with brand new appliances! You will love your time outdoors relaxing on the deck with owner's suite access overlooking a fenced backyard! Carpet is new in 3 bedrooms, Interior freshly painted, New blinds throughout, New Hot Water Tank Nov 2023, 1 Year Home Warranty included!
